                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-107-18511215 t18511215-107-punishment-29"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">PEACOCK</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18511215-107-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18511215-107-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18511215-107-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There were two other indictments against the prisoners, to which George Curtis pleaded Guilty, and</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PARNELL</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">offered no evidence against the others</hi>.)</p>
